    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required Gradation levels at MRL 2. Six factors are accepted as not-assessed per MRL 2 scoping. Validation results demonstrate RH index prediction within 8.3% mean absolute error against the FDA benchmark, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all 5 CPB operating points. The credibility evidence is assessed as sufficient to support the COU decision. Note: validation runs were executed under solver build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2; the production solver is ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7. Per build team memo BT-2026-0312, the rc2-to-release delta is limited to documentation strings and a licence-check patch with no physics impact. The credibility team accepts this assertion and considers the validation evidence applicable to the production build without re-execution.",
